Scaffold a new plugin or registry from a built-in template

Usage: influxdb3-plugin new <TEMPLATE> [PATH] [OPTIONS]
       influxdb3-plugin new list [OPTIONS]

Commands:
  list  List available templates
  help  Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help  Print help

Run `influxdb3-plugin new list` to see available templates, or `influxdb3-plugin new <template> --help` for per-template options. Pass `--output` after the template name (e.g. `new registry --output json`).
